public abstract class BusinessCommand<S>
extends Command<Business,S>

Base command for Business method invocations.
Overrides doPreExecution() method to make the receiver parameter mandatory not null to the invoker.

Provides a protected field named "business" to its subclasses. This field is initialized in the doPreExecution() method.
